
# MySQL Learning Diary

## Day 3: CRUD Operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete)

### Objective

* Table mein data insert karna
* Data retrieve (read) karna
* Data update aur delete karna

---

## Concepts Learned

### What is CRUD?

* Create → Data insert karna
* Read → Data dekhna
* Update → Data change karna
* Delete → Data remove karna

---

## Commands Practiced

### Insert Data

```sql id="5t9n2p"
INSERT INTO students (id, name, age, marks)
VALUES (1, 'Rahul', 20, 85.5);
```

Multiple rows insert:

```sql id="l4y0sb"
INSERT INTO students VALUES
(2, 'Aman', 21, 78.0),
(3, 'Neha', 19, 92.3);
```

---

### Read Data

```sql id="aqf6d0"
SELECT * FROM students;
```

Specific columns:

```sql id="dtrc3l"
SELECT name, marks FROM students;
```

---

### Update Data

```sql id="t8w3e2"
UPDATE students
SET marks = 90
WHERE id = 1;
```

---

### Delete Data

```sql id="xk2m9v"
DELETE FROM students
WHERE id = 2;
```

---

## Practice Tasks

### Task 1

Students table mein 3 records insert karo

```sql id="d4h8kp"
INSERT INTO students VALUES
(4, 'Karan', 22, 67.5),
(5, 'Simran', 20, 88.0),
(6, 'Priya', 21, 91.2);
```

---

### Task 2

Sirf naam aur marks display karo

```sql id="0p8zre"
SELECT name, marks FROM students;
```

---

### Task 3

Kisi ek student ke marks update karo

```sql id="j9s2wl"
UPDATE students
SET marks = 95
WHERE id = 4;
```

---

### Task 4

Ek record delete karo

```sql id="c7m1qa"
DELETE FROM students
WHERE id = 5;
```

---

## Challenges Faced

* WHERE clause miss karne se pura data change/delete ho sakta hai
* Update aur delete mein dhyaan dena zaroori hai

---

## Learning Outcome

* Data insert, read, update aur delete karna aa gaya
* SQL ka real use samajh aaya
* Query likhne mein confidence increase hua

